<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Main Website | <%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6200ea, #03dac6);
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container h1 {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #000;
        }
        .container p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .image-gallery {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .image-gallery img {
            width: 250px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Website</h1>
        <p>We are dedicated to providing top-notch services and innovative solutions. Explore our platform and learn more about what we offer.</p>
        <div class="image-gallery">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1465146344425-f00d5f5c8f07?q=80&w=1776&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Nature">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488590528505-98d2b5aba04b?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Technology">
            <img src="https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1661764256397-af154e87b1b3?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Business">
        </div>
        <p></p>
        <p></p>
        <p class="additional-text">Discover the latest trends, innovations, and updates in the industry. Stay connected and informed with our expertly curated content.</p>
